\ProvidesPackage{myTRSsymbols}[2021/10/26 package myTRSsymbols; Support Term Rewriting symbols, and my own semantic valid transformation symbols. Based on Das extpfeil-Package, extensible arrows: https://www.ctan.org/tex-archive/macros/latex/contrib/extpfeil.]	 

